";; appendix-05-blues-progression.slat
;; Book of Music — Appendix 5: The Blues Progression and What It Holds
;; Written 2026-07-13. Author: Lacuna Labs Engineering.
;; Sources: Grove Music Online 'Blues'; Elijah Wald, Escaping the Delta:
